Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.64,0:01:39.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.91,0:01:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.91,0:01:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.80,0:01:45.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Armin Arlert from Shiganshina, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.87,0:01:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That so? A name fit for a retard!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.98,0:01:49.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Your parents named you that?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.21,0:01:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,It was my grandfather, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.17,0:01:53.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Arlert, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.83,0:01:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To contribute to humanity's victory, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.15,0:01:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,How very admirable.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.84,0:01:59.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You should make first-rate Titan feed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.55,0:02:01.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Third squad! About face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.42,0:02:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,And who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.69,0:02:05.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.40,0:02:07.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Thomas Wagner from Trost, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.65,0:02:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't hear you!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.52,0:02:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Thomas Wagner—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:12.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}I told you to speak up! Go practice \Nsounding off properly in the barracks!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,There he goes again.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.58,0:02:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Next! Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.21,0:02:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Mina Carolina, from Trost, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.46,0:02:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You went through that when you first joined too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.66,0:02:17.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure brings back memories.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.18,0:02:20.37,Default,,0,0,0,,You were born in a pigsty, inferior even to swine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.37,0:02:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! I'm inferior to swine, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:26.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Wrong! I tell you what you are and what you aren't!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.69,0:02:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,What's he trying to accomplish by humiliating them like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.81,0:02:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a rite of passage.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.23,0:02:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Their prior identities are forcibly discarded,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.57,0:02:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,leaving only blank slates from which true soldiers can be produced.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.94,0:02:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}That's a dipshit name! Get lost!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.08,0:02:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a necessary step along the path laid out before them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.58,0:02:35.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why the hell are you even here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.04,0:02:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,To devote myself to the cause of mankind, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.30,0:02:38.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Fourth squad, about face!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.30,0:02:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,But why is he skipping a few recruits?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.60,0:02:47.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who already underwent a rite of passage need not repeat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.23,0:02:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd bet they walked through Hell itself two years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It's written all over their faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.07,0:02:55.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:57.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.99,0:03:00.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Jean Kirstein from Trost, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.57,0:03:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.03,0:03:05.99,Default,,0,0,0,,To join the Military Police Brigade and reside in the Inner District, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.36,0:03:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. So you wanna live in the Inner District?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.50,0:03:12.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.20,0:03:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Who gave you permission to sit?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.32,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can't even handle {\i1}that{\i0}, you'll never make it into the Military Police Brigade!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.24,0:03:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,And who the hell are you? What did you come here for?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.51,0:03:27.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Marco Bott from Jinae, in Wall Rose's Southern District, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.19,0:03:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I came to join the Military Police Brigade and pledge myself to the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.53,0:03:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Is that so? Good man.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.29,0:03:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A noble objective.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.03,0:03:38.47,Default,,0,0,0,,But remember:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.05,0:03:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,the King doesn't want you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.34,0:03:48.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Next, you there! Who the hell are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Connie Springer from Ragako, in Wall Rose's Southern District, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.87,0:03:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen up, Connie Springer!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.67,0:03:57.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This was one of the first things you were taught:
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.84,0:04:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,That salute means you're offering your heart to the King!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.76,0:04:06.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Is your heart on your right side, shithead?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.65,0:04:19.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, you. What the hell are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.28,0:04:25.32,Default,,0,0,0,,You! I'm talking to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.32,0:04:26.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the fuck are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.57,0:04:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Sasha Blouse from Dauper, in Wall Rose's Southern District, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.21,0:04:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Sasha Blouse...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.38,0:04:39.30,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that you're holding in your right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.30,0:04:40.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A steamed potato, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.11,0:04:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,I came across it in the kitchen, so I picked it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.77,0:04:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean you {\i1}stole{\i0} it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:48.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.53,0:04:50.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you eating a potato right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.30,0:04:54.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to eat it while it was still warm,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.47,0:04:56.73,Default,,0,0,0,,so I figured it was now or never, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.59,0:05:00.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No... I don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.62,0:05:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you eating a potato?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.54,0:05:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you asking why people eat potatoes in general, sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.91,0:05:25.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Take a half for yourself, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.14,0:05:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Half...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, that potato girl's still running.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.59,0:05:40.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow... She's been at it for five hours now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:44.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Her reaction when he told her to run until she dropped
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.38,0:05:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,was nothing compared to when he told her she's not getting any food.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:54.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Dauper is a small village of hunters up in the mountains, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.15,0:05:56.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.53,0:06:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Dropouts. They requested a transfer to the reclaimed lands.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.50,0:06:03.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Already? It's only the first day...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.71,0:06:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That's just how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.15,0:06:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The weak have no choice but to leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.50,0:06:12.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They'd prefer picking up rocks and pulling weeds...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.86,0:06:17.35,Default,,0,0,0,,That reminds me. We never heard where you're from or anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.35,0:06:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm from Shiganshina, same as him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.20,0:06:22.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.55,0:06:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.50,0:06:25.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you were there on {\i1}that{\i0} day too?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.70,0:06:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.68,0:06:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you see it? The Colossal Titan?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.32,0:06:31.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:37.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I already told you. I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.02,0:06:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.18,0:06:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How big was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.83,0:06:43.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Tall enough to look right over the wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.02,0:06:44.03,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.03,0:06:46.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard it could straddle the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.01,0:06:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Me too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.08,0:06:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard the same in my village!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.80,0:06:51.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it wasn't {\i1}that{\i0} gigantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.65,0:06:53.31,Default,,0,0,0,,What did it look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.01,0:06:57.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It had barely any skin and its mouth was enormous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.75,0:07:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the Armored Titan that broke through Wall Maria?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.84,0:07:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though people call it that, it looked like a normal Titan to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.36,0:07:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Th-Then, what are normal Titans like?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.92,0:07:19.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys, that's enough questions.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.81,0:07:21.64,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure he has memories he'd rather not relive.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.21,0:07:23.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for being so—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:24.66,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:32.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, Titans aren't such a big deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.47,0:07:36.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Once we master operating the Three Dimensional Maneuver Gear,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.54,0:07:38.22,Default,,0,0,0,,they'll be no match for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.06,0:07:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We finally have the chance to become soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.75,0:07:44.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I just swallowed wrong earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll join the Recon Corps and purge the world of the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.94,0:07:50.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll exterminate them—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.36,0:07:51.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Dude, are you nuts?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.74,0:07:56.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you just say you want to join the Recon Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.53,0:07:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn straight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.35,0:08:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're planning to join the Military Police Brigade to take it easy, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.50,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just an honest fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.19,0:08:11.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's preferable to acting tough when you're actually scared shitless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.47,0:08:15.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You got something to say?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.18,0:08:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.94,0:08:19.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? I wasn't really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.70,0:08:31.62,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.62,0:08:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I wasn't trying to judge how you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.26,0:08:36.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just let it go.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.64,0:08:41.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, same here. I overreacted.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.39,0:08:57.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:05.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, it's just that I've never seen you around, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.79,0:09:10.78,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry... Your black hair is really gorgeous.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.78,0:09:12.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.66,0:09:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever. Give me a break!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.73,0:09:26.46,Default,,0,0,0,,You're always so impulsive when you get emotional.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.46,0:09:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Not this again.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.46,0:09:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't you be worrying more about your hair and less about me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.71,0:09:35.56,Default,,0,0,0,,It's long enough to get tangled when we're doing 3D maneuver training.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.25,0:09:38.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine, I'll cut it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.80,0:09:42.05,Default,,0,0,0,,How short do you think it should be?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.56,0:09:49.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.11,0:09:51.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you just wipe on me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.06,0:09:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,My faith in others.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.87,0:10:24.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Bread?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.04,0:10:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,That was all I could save you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.10,0:10:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But... You should drink some water first.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.92,0:10:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,God? Are you... God?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.82,0:10:43.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.19,0:10:49.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Well... She's been running all day long.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.63,0:10:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like you're just trying to do a good deed.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.29,0:11:02.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Was it just for the sake of potato girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.13,0:11:05.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Were your efforts worthwhile?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.29,0:11:10.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.73,0:11:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's just carry her back to her bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.13,0:11:18.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to do a good deed as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm just doing her a favor to put her in my debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.25,0:11:24.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Her stupidity could come in handy later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,First, your aptitude will be tested.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.75,0:11:34.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Those who fail are not even worthy to serve as bait.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.79,0:11:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Failures will be sent to the reclaimed lands!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.77,0:11:41.08,Default,,0,0,0,,This exercise is the most basic of the fundamentals,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.08,0:11:44.20,Default,,0,0,0,,yet already you can ascertain who's \Nadept at using the 3D Maneuver Gear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.74,0:11:49.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at her. She's hardly wobbling at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.74,0:11:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,She intuitively knows what she's supposed to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.41,0:11:55.65,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the definition of talent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.77,0:11:59.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like we've got some quality new blood this year.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.64,0:12:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Uh, what about him?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.48,0:12:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's talented in his own way.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.50,0:12:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Sometimes, no matter how hard people try, they're incapable of success.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell are you doing, Erin Jaeger?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.92,0:12:14.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your upper body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.97,0:12:19.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}What? How do I do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.28,0:12:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You've gotta be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.69,0:12:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it if you focus on the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.33,0:12:39.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about being perfect for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.97,0:12:45.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay attention to keeping your balance centered, and rest your weight on the waist and sole belts.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.97,0:12:48.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay calm and you can pull it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.09,0:12:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Even I managed to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.04,0:12:52.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, I think I've got it this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.96,0:12:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Lift me up, Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Look at him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.93,0:13:15.81,Default,,0,0,0,,He talked a big game yesterday, saying he'd kill all the Titans.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He'll be working at the reclaimed lands after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.30,0:13:21.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Useless kids don't deserve food.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.85,0:13:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.34,0:13:26.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let their trash-talk get to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.53,0:13:29.01,Default,,0,0,0,,You still have tomorrow to get better.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.49,0:13:30.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so pathetic...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.46,0:13:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,At this rate, I'll never be able to slaughter them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.90,0:13:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You should just forget about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.17,0:13:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.92,0:13:42.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I said you should forget about becoming a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.51,0:13:46.85,Default,,0,0,0,,There's more to fighting than throwing your life away.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.85,0:13:51.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten all the anguish I endured that day?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:53.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you seriously think I'll give up that easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.98,0:13:57.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's got nothing to do with how determined you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.37,0:13:59.19,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.75,0:14:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Because whether you can become a soldier or not isn't your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.58,0:14:15.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not telling you to leave for the reclaimed lands on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an8}Let's go, Armin.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.85,0:14:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.62,0:14:21.13,Default,,0,0,0,,If that happens, I'll come with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.30,0:14:29.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Um... So...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.05,0:14:32.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Does that mean I can take this?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:53.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You're asking me for tips?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.12,0:14:57.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry bro, I'm naturally gifted. I think you just gotta 'feel' it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.68,0:15:04.63,Default,,0,0,0,,How about you give me a tip... on how to stay sane after completely humiliating yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.63,0:15:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Guys... I'm literally begging you here!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.48,0:15:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But weren't you the one saying "the untalented should just leave"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.48,0:15:18.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, no. Wasn't it "the weak have no choice but to leave"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Which one was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.52,0:15:24.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Please! I heard both of you are really good!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.77,0:15:26.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Bertolt! Reiner!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.72,0:15:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry, but I don't think there's really a trick to hanging still.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.74,0:15:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any helpful advice to give you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.28,0:15:36.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.31,0:15:38.23,Default,,0,0,100,,Then you'll just have to bet it all on tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.71,0:15:41.62,Default,,0,0,100,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.62,0:15:44.03,Default,,0,0,100,,Both of you are from Shiganshina, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.03,0:15:45.59,Default,,0,0,100,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.59,0:15:48.65,Default,,0,0,100,,Then you should know firsthand how dreadful the Titans are.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.03,0:15:51.30,Default,,0,0,100,,Why would you want to become soldiers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:15:59.52,Default,,0,0,100,,Unlike Eren, I haven't seen the horror of the Titans with my own eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.84,0:16:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,But after witnessing the monarchy's insane attempt to recover the wall,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.85,0:16:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,I just couldn't stand by and do nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.97,0:16:09.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.61,0:16:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What about the two of you?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.39,0:16:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Reiner and I are from a small mountain village south-east of Wall Maria.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.20,0:16:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,You're from {\i1}that{\i0} place?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:25.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Unlike the bustling riverside towns, our village didn't get word quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.69,0:16:29.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The Titans themselves arrived before the news did.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.48,0:16:31.93,Default,,0,0,0,,It was around dawn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.09,0:16:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,The livestock started getting agitated, and the ground began rumbling in the strangest way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.86,0:16:44.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Soon, I realized what I was hearing were footsteps.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.63,0:16:47.80,Default,,0,0,0,,When I rushed to open the windows...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.44,0:17:01.19,Default,,0,0,0,,After that, I don't really remember what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.78,0:17:03.52,Default,,0,0,0,,It was all very chaotic.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.52,0:17:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, why are you dredging that back up?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.73,0:17:14.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyways, my point is that you guys are different from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.78,0:17:16.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Them?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.84,0:17:20.38,Default,,0,0,0,,The people here who've never experienced the horror of the Titans firsthand.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.38,0:17:21.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.01,0:17:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Most of them are here to protect their social status.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.86,0:17:37.66,Default,,0,0,0,,In these times, choosing to work in a factory when you reach age 12 is considered cowardly,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.66,0:17:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,so many enlist in the Training Corps instead.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.84,0:17:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Not that I'm really much different from them.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.29,0:17:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,I enrolled to join the Military Police Brigade so that I could live safely in the Inner District.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,If that goal proves unattainable, I may just resign.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.42,0:17:58.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have a strong spirit.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.45,0:18:03.65,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no shame in valuing your own life.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.52,0:18:10.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm going back to my abandoned homeland.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.24,0:18:13.31,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I care about.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.87,0:18:17.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll do it, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.76,0:18:20.73,Default,,0,0,0,,And you?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you choose to enlist?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.56,0:18:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.66,0:18:34.84,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought that I had to kill them all...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.92,0:18:39.80,Default,,0,0,0,,That I must exterminate all the Titans myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.80,0:18:42.18,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what I believed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.86,0:18:51.46,Default,,0,0,0,,So your heart never wavered, even after encountering a Titan?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,No. For now, I'm just worried about becoming a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.93,0:19:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Start off by re-adjusting the belts.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.52,0:19:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be just fine tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.25,0:19:24.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I have faith in you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.66,0:19:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger, was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.66,0:19:29.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.31,0:19:32.27,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Reiner Braun, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.57,0:19:45.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren Jaeger, are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.62,0:19:46.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.91,0:19:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'll do it... I have to do it.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.32,0:19:52.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I might not have the talent,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.16,0:19:55.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I'm more determined than anyone else here!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.25,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.78,0:20:07.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the theory.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.27,0:20:08.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know the basics.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.23,0:20:12.52,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's all I've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.31,0:20:16.09,Default,,0,0,0,,This is {\i1}my{\i0} weapon!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.99,0:20:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.91,0:20:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No... I can still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.09,0:20:40.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Let him down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:48.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I can still...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.04,0:20:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Wagner, lend Jaeger your belt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.22,0:20:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.50,0:21:03.24,Default,,0,0,0,,The equipment was faulty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.86,0:21:07.95,Default,,0,0,0,,The metal fittings on your belt were damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.95,0:21:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen damage to these parts before.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:14.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose we'll need to update the maintenance checklist.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.79,0:21:18.56,Default,,0,0,0,,So he actually succeeded... even with faulty equipment...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.56,0:21:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.25,0:21:23.22,Default,,0,0,0,,S-So... what's your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.08,0:21:25.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're good to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.57,0:21:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay resolute and train hard!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I did it. I actually did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.94,0:21:33.52,Default,,0,0,0,,See that, Mikasa? I can do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.07,0:21:35.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can fight the Titans!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.71,0:21:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't need to depend on you anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.28,0:21:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow he pulled it off...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.34,0:21:45.73,Default,,0,0,0,,He's challenging you with his eyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.73,0:21:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:48.74,0:21:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that we don't have to be separated, he's relieved.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.84,0:22:02.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Grisha, today your son has become a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:55.87,0:23:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Upon graduating from the Training Corps,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.41,0:24:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Eren witnesses mankind with its dignity restored.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.50,0:24:06.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Yet the moment he becomes certain they can vanquish the Titans,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.48,0:24:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,mankind is taught a hard lesson.
